spanGrp.span: I have got a mother, father and a grandmother and we plant potatoes and we profit from it.

išlirıh torpah aldıh äkirıh kartol arpa iš kömäk ederım babama inäk_minägınän ištem yaširıh

I have got two sisters, I studied at school in Russian.
